    "uid":"25q:25l",
    "sourceUid":"25q",
    "name":"Medium Heating",
    "description":"When the system is active and is in the MEDIUM temperature stage:\n- it shall request the medium temperature level based on the parameter \"TempStg_Med\"\n- only the first two LEDs shall be enabled",
    "externalUUID":"subterra:data-service:objects:/default/seatheater${WorkItem}SEAT-85",
